Pepsi has officially signed on 4 DJs as Pepsi DJ ambassador with a cool campaign tagged “Refresh The Mix”. The new Pepsi DJ ambassadors are DJ Spinall, Dj Cuppy, Dj Obi and Dj Xclusive.  Watch the video below  With the Refresh the mix campaign and the signing of the top DJs, brand Pepsi is set to take their music association to another level. Refresh the mix with the new Pepsi DJ ambassadors also means more music, more musical revolutions, more epic vibes, exciting mixes and more refreshing moments in music.     Follow Pepsi Naija on social media to keep up with the movement as things unfold. Its Pepsi Nigeria on facebook and @Pepsi_naija on instagram and twitter. The hashtag is #RefreshTheMix #PepsiDJAmbassadors. Get set to #REFRESHTHEMIX with Pepsi. The post #RefreshTheMix: Spinall, Cuppy, Obi and Xclusive are new Pepsi DJ Ambassadors appeared first on 360Nobs.com. Do you have something awesome to share with the world? Click here to share Do you ever have any question about anything you wish to ask and get answer? Click here to ask Follow us on twitter @NigeriaTodayNG Also, Like us on facebook This post was syndicated from 360Nobs.com. Click here to read the full text on the original website.